    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599700/extras/81f04e60b9fcf8c9e55bcf3ca4a9e1c3.avif?t=1770017785\" width=1560 height=336 /></span>Bianca 的父亲是一名神秘现象调查者，因为需要出一趟远门，便拜托女儿打扫房子，尤其是阁楼。在整理过程中，Bianca 发现了一台奇怪而古老的相机，并开始用它在家中四处拍照。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >原本平凡的经历却发生了巨大的转变——照片中出现了她父亲一直提起、而她从未真正相信过的存在：来自冥界的灵体。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bianca 并没有感到害怕，反而觉得这一切令人着迷。然而，她拍到的其中一位存在并不喜欢 Bianca 的新兴趣，于是决定不惜一切代价让她删除这些照片，甚至假装成她最好的朋友，陪伴她整整一周。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她能说服 Bianca 吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bianca 能在短短一周内找到真爱吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快来体验这款短小可爱的百合兽人题材 Kinetic Novel，感受女孩与爱情的故事吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599700/extras/e8c9b3362674053efb6ac2d45633fc65.avif?t=1770017785\" width=1560 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599700/extras/a63c54f38c0483f2879e724c6b4993dd.webp?t=1770017785\" width=17 height=18 /></span>温暖人心的短篇百合故事</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599700/extras/a63c54f38c0483f2879e724c6b4993dd.webp?t=1770017785\" width=17 height=18 /></span>支持自动模式的 Kinetic Novel</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599700/extras/a63c54f38c0483f2879e724c6b4993dd.webp?t=1770017785\" width=17 height=18 /></span>兽人风格 CG 插画</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599700/extras/a63c54f38c0483f2879e724c6b4993dd.webp?t=1770017785\" width=17 height=18 /></span>Stea